      * EMPLECPY - Employee Record COPYBOOK
      * 8-byte English name: EMPLECPY
      * Fixed Block record structure for EMP.INFO dataset
      * Record length: 80 bytes
       
      * Employee Information Record Layout
       01  EMPLOYEE-RECORD.
           05  EMP-ID              PIC X(5).
           05  EMP-NAME            PIC X(20).
           05  EMP-EMAIL           PIC X(20).
           05  EMP-FILLER          PIC X(35).
       
      * Working storage for employee processing
       01  WS-EMPLOYEE-WORK.
           05  WS-EMP-ID           PIC X(5).
           05  WS-EMP-NAME         PIC X(20).
           05  WS-EMP-EMAIL        PIC X(20).
           05  WS-RECORD-COUNT     PIC 9(3) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-EOF-FLAG         PIC X VALUE 'N'.
           05  WS-FILE-STATUS      PIC XX.
       
      * Display formatting fields
       01  WS-DISPLAY-FIELDS.
           05  WS-HEADER-LINE      PIC X(80).
           05  WS-DATA-LINE        PIC X(80).
           05  WS-SEPARATOR-LINE   PIC X(80) VALUE ALL '-'.